name: Headliner
0:
”Alexa, ask Headliner News for the latest from BBC News”
”Alexa, ask Headliner News for the breaking news from The Guardian UK”
”Alexa, ask Headliner News for the news from TechCrunch”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: headliner news
des:
Headliner provides the latest headlines from over 50 major news outlets. Choose from a list including sources like:

Associated Press
BBC
Breitbart News
CNN
Engadget
Financial Times
National Geographic
Polygon
Reuters
TechCrunch
The Economist
The Guardian UK
The New York Times
The Wall Street Journal
... and many more! 

Powered by NewsAPI.org
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
